divs: Sighting DetailsI was Taking my dogs out to pee and I looked up at the Stars. I noticed one of them was flickering and it started to sway from side to side. I also noticed 2 more flickering but the were not moving. The one that was moving was giving off a strobe like light. The light was a redish color
